Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.82,0:13:00.88,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.36,0:13:03.82,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.92,0:13:29.66,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,One frankfurter, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.84,0:13:31.24,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,One frankfurter!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.48,0:13:32.91,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.63,0:13:47.20,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.64,0:13:49.84,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Maids, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.84,0:13:51.85,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Those clothes are cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.85,0:13:54.14,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nayu-chan made them for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.57,0:13:56.33,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayama-san did a lot of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.33,0:13:57.78,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.52,0:14:05.01,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizuno-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.01,0:14:06.05,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.05,0:14:06.99,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.60,0:14:10.18,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.28,0:14:18.17,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Get Hayama-san right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.84,0:14:23.38,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.60,0:14:26.88,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Tsukamoto-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.32,0:14:31.80,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,The school's name is in here. On top of that, you're calling yourselves the Underwear Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.96,0:14:36.27,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've also heard that you're participating in the cultural festival without permission...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.32,0:14:38.67,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,by helping the Acting Club with their costumes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.80,0:14:39.69,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.33,0:14:41.70,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,The play is canceled.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.19,0:14:45.07,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! You don't need to go that far!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.73,0:14:50.24,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't allow a delinquent club to participate in school activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.39,0:14:54.73,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.73,0:14:56.60,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Mizuno-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.32,0:15:01.02,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,The members of the Acting Club and Underwear Society...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.02,0:15:04.56,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,have both put a lot of effort into this cultural festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.56,0:15:07.08,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be unfair to stop them at this point!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.35,0:15:16.47,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,These girls have worked hard to create good costumes and underwear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.47,0:15:21.65,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,The cultural festival is a place for students to show off the fruits of their labors.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.35,0:15:27.15,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, reconsider your decision until you've seen what these girls have made.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.92,0:15:29.40,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.89,0:15:31.25,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.00,0:15:38.18,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I agree with Mizuno-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.18,0:15:38.87,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.23,0:15:48.52,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, we just got out of our class' shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.61,0:15:55.64,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? You guys seem down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:15:59.23,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.56,0:16:00.64,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.10,0:16:04.51,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Our angelic savior has been captured by a demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.51,0:16:07.23,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's perfect. Looks like you're all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.85,0:16:14.26,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.21,0:16:18.02,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,The play might be canceled.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.84,0:16:22.79,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Amahara-san, I need to speak with you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.64,0:16:26.48,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,About my appearance in a magazine?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.78,0:16:29.36,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then in that case, why don't you just punish me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.79,0:16:31.26,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Amahara-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.30,0:16:34.36,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,What a sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.23,0:16:36.96,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's their fault for letting it get to their heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.15,0:16:38.25,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.32,0:16:41.62,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tanihara-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.91,0:16:43.73,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,You came!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.73,0:16:46.28,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen you since graduation. How have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.02,0:16:49.32,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.42,0:16:51.66,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, Hayama-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.66,0:16:53.03,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayama?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.71,0:16:58.03,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukamoto-sensei, these are the costumes these girls made.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.74,0:17:01.04,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.04,0:17:05.26,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,She said a delinquent club can't participate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.26,0:17:06.51,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.51,0:17:15.06,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,But Mizuno-sensei asked her to hold her judgment until after she looked at the costumes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.67,0:17:17.97,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,The curves really are beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.82,0:17:23.43,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,The lace has been layered skillfully. It's wonderfully spreading.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.87,0:17:26.56,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What do you think, Tsukamoto-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.50,0:17:37.87,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.28,0:17:39.44,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Hayama in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.87,0:17:41.31,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.56,0:17:45.29,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my homeroom teacher from elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.91,0:17:50.30,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terribly sorry one of my students has been causing so much trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.30,0:17:51.74,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayama, you apologize as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.85,0:17:56.37,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you're running an Underwear Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.13,0:17:59.64,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are these perverted clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.49,0:18:03.28,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I had high hopes from you since your grades were good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.28,0:18:06.06,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you're chasing after boys already!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.06,0:18:08.60,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this all you think about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.07,0:18:11.44,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an embarrassment to our school!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.99,0:18:17.57,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is underwear really something to be ashamed of?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.99,0:18:19.91,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying you don't wear underwear?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.91,0:18:20.74,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.74,0:18:24.58,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,The Underwear Society does nothing more than study underwear!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.58,0:18:26.50,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd never do anything immoral!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.50,0:18:32.00,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! We've learned a lot of useful information about underwear!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.53,0:18:36.29,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I used to think that underwear was perverted as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.29,0:18:40.89,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,but I learned the importance of wearing proper underwear for my developing body!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.25,0:18:45.22,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking to Hayama! You've got nothing to do with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.75,0:18:47.73,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.49,0:18:52.98,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Underwear is something everyone wears. It isn't something to be ashamed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.27,0:18:57.82,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,On that note, you're the one who has nothing to do with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.23,0:19:00.70,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.17,0:19:05.70,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, there's something wrong with this school's teachers!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.24,0:19:13.34,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Tanihara-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.55,0:19:17.53,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Tsukamoto-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.72,0:19:21.52,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I still refuse to acknowledge the Underwear Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.64,0:19:27.19,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I'm willing to overlook the magazine incident this one time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.19,0:19:29.14,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll also allow the play.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.52,0:19:32.65,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.12,0:19:35.65,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Tsukamoto-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.65,0:19:39.59,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then these girls will be able to continue their work, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.14,0:19:44.52,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,The school has no right to prevent students from studying underwear on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.15,0:19:48.97,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great, Nayu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.97,0:19:49.62,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.62,0:19:51.99,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm am not done talking yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.47,0:19:58.91,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Amahara-san, make sure you get the school's permission before doing anything again! You girls, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.56,0:20:01.99,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try to stop me, Sharuru-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.99,0:20:06.32,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Angela, this school doesn't need swords!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.54,0:20:08.93,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Love. Love is what it needs!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.28,0:20:15.01,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Warriors from another school have invaded ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.31,0:20:18.78,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep fighting among yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.78,0:20:22.28,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,This school will be ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.81,0:20:34.34,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad Jinguji took my spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.67,0:20:36.45,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Though she can't act well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.31,0:20:39.30,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.56,0:20:47.22,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad we got to put on the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.85,0:20:50.10,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was worried what would happen for a while there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.10,0:20:53.69,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, everyone. This cultural festival has been a lot of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.40,0:20:56.06,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,thank you too, Amahara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.97,0:21:03.75,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like we get to keep running the Underwear Society, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.83,0:21:05.72,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are we going to do next year?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.72,0:21:06.95,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Next year...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.60,0:21:08.80,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nayu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.80,0:21:09.95,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.56,0:21:13.14,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Next... year...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.76,0:21:16.25,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Spit it out already!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.89,0:21:18.22,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.77,0:21:21.39,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to tell them eventually!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.19,0:21:23.70,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nayu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.41,0:21:26.52,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for keeping it a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.87,0:21:28.76,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.19,0:21:31.43,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoto? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.67,0:21:36.48,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nayu hasn't told anyone, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.85,0:21:40.15,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think the Underwear Society knows, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.93,0:21:45.90,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,It came up a few years ago, but I refused at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.33,0:21:50.55,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nayu found out about it afterwards and seemed to be bothered by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.80,0:21:54.54,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,So... When will you be going?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.94,0:21:56.17,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.34,0:21:59.84,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm transferring.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.59,0:23:44.26,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sad about you leaving, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.26,0:23:47.43,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always cherish the times we spent together.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.43,0:23:50.28,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I got tear stains on my favorite underwear.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.28,0:23:52.20,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're talking about underwear at the very end?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.20,0:23:54.37,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't miss the next episode of {\i1}Chu-Bra!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.55,0:23:57.26,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,
